Class AbstractClientHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se.eliafinazzigrazioli.adrenaline.server.AbstractClientHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientHandlerRMI, ClientHandlerSocket 

    public abstract class AbstractClientHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Represents the joint between the different networks implementations. It plays the role of a VirtualView in the MVC client-server pattern.
